data.description: Let's talk about location, location, location. This home is conveniently located near schools, parks, shopping, and minutes from I355 just to name a few. As you pull up to this home, you will find it nestled amongst mature trees and notice a newer roof, driveway, windows. Did you need a Fenced yard, check out the space in the backyard which is fully fenced, large shed and huge patio for all your entertainment desires. All this and we haven't walked thru the front door. Once inside you will find a large family room off the dining room and kitchen. Need a first floor bedroom? Check that box as well! As you venture upstairs, you will find 4 other spacious bedrooms with tons of hardwood flooring. Need storage space, check out the crawl space that is extra deep. Enjoy Fitness or swimming? Just behind the homes across the street you will find an AMAZING complex awaiting you!
